Production envireonment EC2 aws instance with nginx as httpserver + uwsgi + django

The postgresql database is executed in a separate RDS aws instance



For backend deployment I need:

/home/USER/supervisord.conf
/home/USER/uwsgi.ini
/etc/nginx/sites-available/wifibytes-backend.nginx.conf

The examples are not general configurations should be customized for your solution is only a concrete example
Install and configure nginx, supervisord and be sure uwsgi python packege is installed in your pthon env. 


For frontend deployment I need:

/etc/nginx/sites-available/wifibytes-frontend.nginx.conf


 

